com.amplifyframework.datastore.appsync

Class AppSyncClient

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.amplifyframework.datastore.appsync.AppSyncClient
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AppSync

    public final class AppSyncClient
extends java.lang.Object
implements AppSync
    An implementation of the AppSync client interface. This implementation adds business rules on top of the generic GraphQL behaviors in the ApiCategoryBehavior. AppSync requests are formed as raw GraphQL document strings, using the AppSyncRequestFactory. The requests are not generic GraphQL, and contain AppSync-specific details like protocol-specific operation names (create, update, delete), assumptions about the structure of data types (unique IDs, versioning information), etc.
